&lt;p&gt;
&lt;a href=&#34;https://docs.n8n.io/hosting/installation/npm/#install-globally-with-npm&#34;&gt;Install globally with npm&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
